data.description:
Come and take a look at his georgous property in the heart of Fareast.  This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath property is perfect for any family looking to settle down in the east side of town.  Solar panels and HVAC were recently installed which provide energy-efficient comfort.  With easy access to Loop 375 and a major hospital, you'll have no trouble getting where you need to go. Plus, being so close to schools, shopping centers, and Fort Bliss gives the convenience of having everything you need just a short drive away. 
For those looking for outdoor activities, the large backyard provides ample room to entertain guests or just enjoy a relaxing afternoon in the sun. With so much to offer, this property is an unbeatable deal on the east side of town! Don't miss out on your chance to call it home.  Come take a look today and make this home yours!
